- - Simple word guessing game, the theme is movie genres.
- 4 total genres to guess from: horror, romance, action, comedy
- 3 total chances to guess the word; if a letter is inputted, it will display the occurences of that letter in the answer. Typing a letter or a word uses 1 total chance.
- Single player game. 
- The game does NOT tell the player the position of letters in the word.
- includes code that uses Pandas to create a leaderboard of attemped scores, players can identify themselves by typing in their name.
- Credit: Jodi Aryee helped during Paired programming..
